comment: RHH shows Jones (HOU) and Griffin (LAC) tangle momentarily, with Griffin lifting Jones's arms toward himself as he runs through.
RATR shows Ariza (HOU) is jumping toward Barnes (LAC) and turning in the air as Barnes attempts his layup.

Paul (LAC) does not affect Harden's (HOU) RSBQ on his drive into the paint. A defensive player is permitted to momentarily touch an opponent with his hand anywhere on the court as long as he does not affect the opponent's RSBQ.
LATR shows Jordan (LAC) jump vertically and make incidental contact with Motiejunas (HOU) that does not affect his RSBQ or shot attempt.
Jones (HOU) establishes a position in front of Griffin (LAC), who dribbles into him.
Motiejunas (HOU) is vertical in his attempt to defend Paul's (LAC) layup attempt. Paul kicks his leg out unnaturally, but the kick does not hit or affect Motiejunas's ability to defend.
Harden (HOU) reaches in and grabs Paul (LAC), who tries to maintain a legal guarding position.
LATR shows Paul (LAC) dislodge Harden (HOU) after he secures the loose ball.
Paul (LAC) and Harden (HOU) lock up momentarily away from the ball and then separate.
Griffin (LAC) holds Harden (HOU), which forces the turnover.
Ariza (HOU) beats Griffin (LAC) to the point of contact and takes the contact while retreating, maintaining legal guarding position.
Ariza (HOU) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and makes a legal reverse pivot while attempting to inbound the ball.
Using a stopwatch, Ariza (HOU) requests a timeout at 4.8 seconds after receiving the ball for the inbounds. He is correctly awarded the timeout.
Jordan (LAC) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
During dead ball situation, Jordan (LAC) raises his elbow to defend the ball. Contact appears accidental.
Ariza (HOU) maintains legal guarding position as Paul (LAC) creates the contact on the drive to the basket.
